title: ctrl 1 key（joke）doesnt work but laugh and dance all works help
body: i use the newst mac os and the ctrl 1 joke doesnt work，all others work i check the setting and dont see  anything i might blind it to{{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}

replies.body: Was it working previously but stopped with your newest OS?  The option to rebind should be available in your binding options.  You'll find it under the Communications tab to see if it's still properly bound or if you want to bind a new key.  I hope that helps!
